verbose_text: Vacuolar Fe uptake was shown to be catalyzed by the ferroportin homologue, AtFPN2 XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, and by the CCC1 like protein AtVIT1 (16); however, the primary substrates of AtFPN2 have been reported to be Ni and Co in addition to Fe XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR.
evidence: Fe uptake was shown to be catalyzed by the ferroportin homologue
